<br>
The test server now has a slide-bar for stackable purchases! This means that you can now purchase up to 20 water, bread, gems, metal bars, etc at one time. All stackable items can now be purchased this way.<br>
<br>
The usual test-disclaimer applies, but this new change should go to the live servers next patch hopefully. <br>
